Name: TCASE-15819 :: Validate file permissions.
Setup: ANF
Test Case URL: -- https://qtest.ngage.netapp.com/p/104/portal/project#tab=testdesign&object=1&id=271803
Notes: 1. Create NFS/SMB volumes. 2. Mount the volumes and create files(file1.txt,file2.txt) in the volumes. 3. Write content into these files and change the permissions of the file. (chmod 777) 4. Take a snapshot.(snap1) 5. Append those files with more content. 6. change the permission of the file(chmod 400) 7. Take a snapshot(snap2) 8. Perform restore operation of the file with snap1 and snap2 9. Validate the file permission of the file1.txt , permission related to file in snap1 is 777 and with snap2 is 400 10. Repeat same with file2.txt giving same original path or different in destination
